# DAY 1

burp suite is a java based framework which is used to pentesting on mobile apps, API's web apps
There are 3 editions of burp suite : 
  1. Community edition 2. professional edition 3. Enterprise edition

  # Installation in windows :
   1) You need to install the Java Runtime first before installing the burp suit as it is a framework based on java then you have to download the exe form the portswigger website.
   2) Then you have to set the proxy in browser and install the CA certificate of the burp in the browser.

# TABS : 
 1) PROXY : All the requests will go trough the burp suite if you turn on the INTERCEPT option from the PROXY tab.
